de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.jrdf2vec.walk_generators.data_structures

Class TripleDataSetMemory

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.jrdf2vec.walk_generators.data_structures.TripleDataSetMemory

  • public class TripleDataSetMemory
extends Object
    There is a distinction in (1) object triples where the object is a URI and (2) datatpye triples where the object is a string. Developer remarks: For reasons of performance, deletions are not possible currently.
